Yeah, it’s a core idea in many Gnostic traditions—that the material world is flawed, created by a lesser god, the Demiurge. So escaping it through secret knowledge, or gnosis, is the goal. Not just qualities, but straight-up doctrine for a lot of them. Though, fair warning, Gnosticism’s not one-size-fits-all; different sects vary on the details.

